DISTRIBUTION, ECOLOGY AND PHENOLOGY. — Poya (Avangui) (
<figureCitation id="77F0B280FFC0F5181DA7390CFD564221" box="[710,761,1577,1601]" captionStart="FIG" captionStartId="16.[426,437,1277,1294]" captionTargetBox="[973,1297,1025,1134]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIG. 7. — Distribution map for subspecies of Gossia clusioides (Brongn. &amp; Gris) N. Snow." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3877408" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3877408/files/figure.png" pageId="17" pageNumber="146">Fig. 7</figureCitation>
); in low forests over ultramafics, to 
<specimenCount id="F9CD658CFFC0F5181EA23961FDA6423B" box="[451,521,1604,1628]" pageId="17" pageNumber="146" type="generic">
<quantity id="283303E0FFC0F5181EA23961FDAA423B" box="[451,517,1604,1628]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" pageId="17" pageNumber="146" unit="m" value="400.0">400 m</quantity>
